# Arithmetic, precedence, numeric tower
2 + 3
=> 5
7 - 10
=> -3
4 * 5
=> 20
10 / 4
=> 2.5
10 / 2
=> 5
2 ^ 10
=> 1024
2 + 3 * 4
=> 14
(2 + 3) * 4
=> 20
2 ^ 3 ^ 2
=> 512
-2 ^ 2
=> -4
1 + 2.0
=> 3
1.5 + 1
=> 2.5
1 / 3
=> 0.333333
2 * 3i
=> 6i
(1 + 2i) + (3 + 4i)
=> 4+6i
(1 + 1i) * (1 - 1i)
=> 2+0i
sqrt(2) ^ 2
=> 2
abs(-5)
=> 5
abs(3 + 4i)
=> 5
